<section class="magroad">
  <div class="magroad-inner">
    <h2>The USA Newcomer Roadmap</h2>
    <p class="magroad-intro">Every successful settlement follows the same financial path. This <strong>moving to America checklist</strong> shows the exact order to tackle each milestone — so you always know what comes next on your journey from arrival to long-term financial success in the United States.</p>
    <div class="magroad-steps">
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">1</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Arrival</h3><p>Land in the USA and gather your key documents.</p></div></div>
      <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">2</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>SSN / ITIN</h3><p>Apply for your Social Security Number, or an ITIN if you are not eligible.</p></div></div>
      <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">3</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Bank Account</h3><p>Open a fee-free or ITIN-friendly checking account.</p></div></div>
      <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">4</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Credit Building</h3><p>Get your first secured card and start building history.</p></div></div>
      <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">5</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Housing</h3><p>Rent an apartment, even without U.S. credit.</p></div></div>
      <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">6</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Healthcare</h3><p>Choose employer, ACA Marketplace, or Medicaid coverage.</p></div></div>
      <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">7</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Employment</h3><p>Find work and get your credentials recognized.</p></div></div>
      <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">8</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Taxes</h3><p>Understand and file your federal and state tax return.</p></div></div>
      <div class="magroad-arrow">&darr;</div>
      <div class="magroad-step"><div class="magroad-num">9</div><div class="magroad-txt"><h3>Long-Term Financial Success</h3><p>Grow savings with a 401(k), IRA, and investing.</p></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="magcta1">
      <h3>Skip the Guesswork on Building Credit</h3>
      <p>Your credit score is the single biggest hurdle newcomers face. Our step-by-step guide shows you the fastest path to a strong U.S. credit profile from scratch — even with no SSN.</p>
      <a href="https://moneyabroadguide.com/how-to-build-credit-in-usa-without-ssn/">Get the Credit-Building eBook &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
